metadata.name: Jungle Misfits #1
metadata.description: In the jungle, apes gather from various factions and clans over the battle royale. A war between the highly advanced apes deep in the rain drop jungle. Over 120 traits built the Jungle Misfits, prepare yourself for war, find your ape and decipher the clues it gives you. A king rising from the battle royale will be crowned!
